juniSmdsAgent.name: juniSmdsAgent

revisions.description: Replaced Unisphere names with Juniper names.
Added support for major and sub interfaces.
The initial release of this management information module.

juniSmdsAgent.contactinfo: Juniper Networks, Inc. Postal: 10 Technology Park Drive Westford, MA 01886-3146 USA Tel: +1 978 589 5800 E-mail: mib@Juniper.net
juniSmdsAgent.description: The agent capabilities definitions for the Switched Multimegabit Data Service (SMDS) management component of the SNMP agent in the Juniper E-series family of products.

juniSmdsAgentV1.name: juniSmdsAgentV1
juniSmdsAgentV1.productrelease:
Version 1 of the Switched Multimegabit Data Service (SMDS) management
        component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version of the SMDS component
        was supported in JUNOSe 3.1 and subsequent 3.x system releases.
juniSmdsAgentV1.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the SMDS application in JUNOSe. These capabilities became obsolete when support was added for major and sub interfaces

juniSmdsAgentV2.name: juniSmdsAgentV2
juniSmdsAgentV2.productrelease:
Version 2 of the Switched Multimegabit Data Service (SMDS) management
        component of the JUNOSe SNMP agent.  This version of the SMDS component
        is supported in JUNOSe 4.0 and subsequent system releases.
juniSmdsAgentV2.description: The MIB supported by the SNMP agent for the SMDS application in JUNOSe.
